<collectingCountry id="F33B763DE3BDFF2BFAF7F8F3BCA0F8EA" box="[1301,1436,1878,1903]" name="Madagascar" pageId="186" pageNumber="187">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
aquatic beetle survey project.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
